class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢班仆街個講法根本就係斷章取義緊斷章取義呢個成語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a521b17f68ced4d78f6305aea468ca013bcb5d","tid":281050,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:58:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家聽下最尾個5分鐘，仲撚仆街<br />\n根本佢就係歸左邊<br />\n陳雲話毓民收美國佬錢，但係佢竟然可以冇反應<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">又話驚毓民係補選支持本民青</span><br />\n即係係由始至終都唔信教主啦</blockquote><br />\n唔係驚啦，教主到時一定講政治倫理支持佢地，佢係知教主取態而唔評論</blockquote><br />\n柒頭，<span style=\"color: red;\">政治倫理同支持兩回事架</span>，當初教主咪又係因為政治倫理而覺得應該俾楊onq入去，結果呢？<br />\n<br />\nsorry，唔記得熱狗最無政治倫理，229即開記者會話每區最少入兩席，咁咪唔叫搶光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃毓民也表示<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民</span>應該支持公民黨派人參加補選，否則是政治不倫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150623/19194767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150623%2F19194767&d=uxwN5JqRpwkDwaH%2Br6EYGm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=6b47a923\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20150623%2F19194767&h=c3784b4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20150623/19194767</a><br />\n<br />\n我都冇鬧教主，你咁激動做咩。</blockquote><br />\n記得你撐熱啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁家傑表示於上周五泛民會議上已得到其他黨派認同楊岳橋為泛民唯一候選人，亦已得到人民力量、社民連及<span style=\"color: red;\">黃毓民支持</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/公民黨楊岳橋宣布參選立法會新界東補選-102700264.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C%E6%9D%B1%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8-102700264.html&d=uxwN5JqRpwkDwaH%2Br6EYGm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=0161afef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/公民黨楊岳橋宣布參選立法會新界東補選-102700264.html</a><br />\n<br />\n是但啦，要分裂慢慢分飽佢，不過唔好痴本民青就得。你知啦，way wrong 抹黑話教主收共產黨錢架嘛。</blockquote><br />\n唔係新聞黎啦<br />\n教主都解釋過係因為旺角初二單野有變數</blockquote><br />\n講緊教主咁講政治倫理，要補選佢撑青政唔出奇，又有人spin政治倫理唔封如會endorse 人"},{"pid":"874d20b7a239aa21ef46eba5ced739aab70f71e6","tid":281050,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"一陣毓民踩場唔知會唔會講依單野"},{"pid":"87e6b757cb027e20db573618a894a101c7cdef35","tid":281050,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>熱狗理解既係 刪剪版=斷章取義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚傳教都要成本聖經由頭到尾一次讀哂<br />\n唔係就斷章取義</blockquote><br />\n可能要聽埋蟲泰一生所講過既說話,唔係都係斷章取義</blockquote><br />\n唉，講黃洋達一直有搵教主唔提，教主敗選去台灣黃洋達去左睇住佢唔提，然後就話泰博為左三萬蚊（實情講緊條同熱普決裂條底線）同佢一齊反骨，唔係斷章取義？"},{"pid":"fc7cc8bee430c394f9483ae9bea872cd078d96bd","tid":281050,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>熱狗理解既係 刪剪版=斷章取義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚傳教都要成本聖經由頭到尾一次讀哂<br />\n唔係就斷章取義</blockquote><br />\n可能要聽埋蟲泰一生所講過既說話,唔係都係斷章取義</blockquote><br />\n唉，講黃洋達一直有搵教主唔提，教主敗選去台灣黃洋達去左睇住佢唔提，然後就話泰博為左三萬蚊（實情講緊條同熱普決裂條底線）同佢一齊反骨，唔係斷章取義？</blockquote><br />\n段17分鐘嘅AVI係乞撚嚟架？柒頭打手"},{"pid":"900cc665edbb00